posts.subject: /loli/ Anime Stream
posts.body:
I was hoping that 8chan would be back by now, but it can't be helped. Guess I'll have to start a stream thread here!

I stream loli anime on cytube every Sunday at 12pm EST. I put up music (almost always 2hu arranges) an hour before the stream, and everyone is encouraged to add their own fun and entertaining videos for the post stream. This week we'll be starting Ryuuou no Oshigoto!
https://cytu.be/r/TewiAnimeStream
